{"tid":1643279,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"立場新聞 - 保險小薯：「罷賣罷食方為上策」錯撚晒","createTime":"2019-10-10T05:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T23:42:02.000Z","uid":300521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5a50fa58302f2fab42ed33ccab8b72e58a6f9c4d","tid":1643279,"uid":300521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:13:48.000Z","msg":"我認同罷買罷食重要，更認同嘅係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">支持黃店</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但內文有一樣無提及嘅，係「續保」嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n我唔相信有任何保險公司再願意同360 美心集團提出續保，同賭錢落海無分別，而續保可能係下年年初，或者第二季。<br />\n<br />\n其實，好可能下年就會見到佢地嘅倒閉潮，因為買唔到店鋪保，佢地仲敢開鋪？<br />\n<br />\nOne More Thing：「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盡快兌晒美心閪餅，東海堂，Starbuck嘅餅券現金券</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n呢啲係佢地預支香港人錢去發展業務，兌晒佢食又好掟又好，換完啲餅佢地要拎錢再生產。如果你潔癖都連食同飲美心集團都想嘔，我嘅建議係：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">「係巿場特價拋售債券，香港人一張都唔好買，留比貪心諗住執到唔嘅藍絲」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n等佢地成為命運共同體，亦可以拎美心賣唔出新嘅債券。"},{"pid":"23a7f48e6aef8d637dccc1bbaa37141b0ccb84c0","tid":1643279,"uid":300521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:15:10.000Z","msg":"留比貪心諗住執到<del>唔</del>金嘅藍絲"},{"pid":"caee6b825b7737985f93c3f4f149118344627563","tid":1643279,"uid":300521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:18:50.000Z","msg":"立場原Post：<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E5%B0%8F%E8%96%AF-%E7%BD%B7%E9%A3%9F%E7%BD%B7%E8%B2%B7-%E6%96%B9%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%8A%E7%AD%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%25B0%258F%25E8%2596%25AF-%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E8%25B2%25B7-%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25AD%2596%2F&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em4lS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=e0e0783f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2